title: [Carrack, Forward Deck]
description: The cannons are mounted on the bulwarks are shadowed beneath a winter white flyrsilk sail billowing from a wooden mast towering overhead.  Crewmen dash back and forth attending to the riggings, while another team moves cargo below deck into the hold.  A crows nest can be spotted high up the mast, ratlines leading up from both sides of the ship to the lookout point.
